thread.title_full: Stateside Bead Supply reviewed by Vivian

author: Vivian
title: Vivian
text: I have been purchasing beads from your company for a number of years now. The quality is very good and the speed at which I receive my orders is excellent! The beads come labeled and neatly packaged. The website improves everytime I visit. Thanks for being a class act!
